[Click Here To Now](https://t.co/wbKQQA6LI8)

It was an extreme blast of nostalgia yet excitement as I watched sonic the Hedgehog movie with my little brother and sister , we thoroughly enjoyed this film. The #SonicMovie LPM (laughs per minute) is off the charts! So great to see people making Sonic their own. I've watched Sonic Movie and this is truly amazing!!

My mother and I loved the movie so much! We saw #SonicMovie last Saturday at the new @PVR movie theater at Durbin Park!  He hasn't stopped talking about it since he saw it yesterday which says a lot.
